schools.name: Joseph L Block Jr High School

data.description: Homey, the main floor has a living room with new vinyl flooring and a new ceiling; an eat-in kitchen, 2 bedrooms, and a fully remodeled bathroom. Upstairs you will find the main bedroom and walk-in closet with new flooring and freshly painted, 3/4th bath. Partially finished basement with large recreation room. New AC compressor. Fully fenced-in yard with 2 car detached garage. There is an above-ground swimming pool too. Affordability meets convenience with great proximity to Lake Michigan and easy access to Hammond, Highland, Munster, Chicago.
